description.narrative: The Project will assist in ensuring sustained equitable and regionally balanced economic growth through infrastructure improvements to Male North Harbor supported by institutional and capacity building initiatives in the domestic maritime transport sector. The expanded capacity of Male North Harbor will reduce transport cost; facilitate inter-island trade; and provide enhanced access to market opportunities for outer atoll population.
